<materialsCitation id="3B041B3AFFF2FFC6F78E55205DFDF2FD" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3804303401" pageId="31" pageNumber="583">“Villa Braga, on the left bank of the Rio Tapajos, just above the first rapids,”</materialsCitation>
